ien" lang="ht" hreflang="ht" class="interlanguage-link-target">Kreyòl ayisyen</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-hy"><a href="https://hy.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D4%B7%D5%B4%D5%AB%D5%AC%D5%AB%D5%B8_%D5%8D%D5%A5%D5%A3%D6%80%D5%A5" title="Էմիլիո Սեգրե — arménien" lang="hy" hreflang="hy" class="interlanguage-link-target">Հայերեն</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-id"><a href="https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emilio_Segr%C3%A8" title="Emilio Segrè — indonésien" lang="id" hreflang="id" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bahasa Indonesia</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-io"><a href="https://io.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emilio_Gino_Segr%C3%A8" title="Emilio Gino Segrè — ido" lang="io" hreflang="io" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ido</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-it"><a href="https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emilio_Segr%C3%A8" title="Emilio Segrè — italien" lang="it" hreflang="it" class="interlanguage-link-target">Italiano</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja"><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%A8%E3%83%9F%E3%83%AA%E3%82%AA%E3%83%BB%E3%82%BB%E3%82%B0%E3%83%AC" title="エミリオ・セグレ — japonais" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" class="interlanguage-link-target">日本語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-jv"><a href="https://jv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emilio_G._Segr%C3%A8" title="Emilio G. Segrè — javanais" lang="jv" hreflang="jv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Jawa</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kk"><a href="https://kk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%AD%D0%BC%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%BE_%D0%94%D0%B6%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%BE_%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%B3%D1%80%D0%B5" title="Эмилио Джино Сегре — kazakh" lang="kk" hreflang="kk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Қазақша</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-km"><a href="https://km.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%9E%A2%E1%9F%81%E1%9E%98%E1%9E%B8%E1%9E%9B%E1%9F%92%E1%9E%99%E1%9E%BC_%E1%9E%A0%E1%9F%92%E1%9E%82%E1%9E%B8%E1%9E%8E%E1%9E%BC_%E1%9E%9F%E1%9F%81%E1%9E%A0%E1%9F%92%E1%9E%82%E1%9