<li><span class="wd_identifiers">Notices dans des dictionnaires ou encyclopédies généralistes<span class="noprint wikidata-linkback"><a href="https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q173028?uselang=fr#identifiers" title="Voir et modifier les données sur Wikidata"><img alt="Voir et modifier les données sur Wikidata" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/10px-Blue_pencil.svg.png" decoding="async" width="10" height="10" style="vertical-align: baseline" class="noviewer" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/15px-Blue_pencil.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Blue_pencil.svg/20px-Blue_pencil.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="600" /></a></span></span>&#160;: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1093/anb/9780198606697.article.1301486"><i>American National Biography</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://brockhaus.de/ecs/enzy/article/segre-emilio-gino"><i>Brockhaus Enzyklopädie</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.deutsche-biographie.de/119166917.html"><i>Deutsche Biographie</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.treccani.it/enciclopedia/emilio-gino-segre_(Dizionario_Biografico)"><i>Dizionario biografico degli italiani</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sapere.it/enciclopedia/Segrè,+Emìlio+Gino.html"><i>Enciclopedia De Agostini</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.britannica.com/biography/Emilio-Segre"><i>Encyclopædia Britannica</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.universalis.fr/encyclopedie/emilio-gino-segre/"><i>Encyclopædia Universalis</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.enciclopedia.cat/EC-GEC-0061682.xml"><i>Gran Enciclopèdia Catalana</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" hr